title: Has Pool Party Started?
body: ^ Has the event started? The "night time" AEST isn't too specific, did they mean at the start of the 15th or at the end of the 15th? Eck.

replies.body: It's likely there will be a big post when it starts.
pretty sure it means around 5-6 pm today, cause that's when it starts to get dark ATM.
